snippet.title: Diana and Roma take care of the cat and new dog balloon dog Squeakee
snippet.description:
This is an ad for Moose Toys. Parents, Squeakee the Balloon Dog is a must-have interactive toy! Part dog, part balloon. Touch and voice recognition. There's never been a toy like Squeakee. Bring one home to guarantee playtime that includes fun, wonderment, and laughter.
